  "texts": [
    "• Informativeness: This metric assesses the extent to which the summary provides a comprehensive understanding of the key points and essential details from the source text.",
    "An informative summary should encapsulate the core ideas, facilitating a clear and precise comprehension of the main arguments and findings of the source document.",
    "• Conciseness: This metric assesses the extent to which the summary excludes less important information from the source text.",
    "A concise summary should effectively eliminate non-essential content from the source document during the generation process.",
    "• Faithfulness: This metric assesses the extent to which the candidate is incorrect in that it contradicts the information from the source document."
  ],
